pc b jd qv pe pf jg qw ph pi gf qx pk pl gi qy pn po gl qz pq pr ps hh bh" =
data-selectable-paragraph=3D"">Putting all of this together, we end up with=
 one <code class=3D"dc ra rb rc rd b">main.py</code> and one <code class=3D=
"dc ra rb rc rd b">index.html</code> per stage, organized as a small Python=
 package with <code class=3D"dc ra rb rc rd b">pyproject.toml</code>. The s=
even <code class=3D"dc ra rb rc rd b">chat-ui-stageN</code> console scripts=
 give you a quick way to jump between stages without remembering uvicorn fl=
ags.</p><p id=3D"7962" class=3D"pw-post-body-paragraph pa pb ij pc b jd pd =
pe pf jg pg ph pi gf pj pk pl gi pm pn po gl pp pq pr ps hh bh" data-select=
able-paragraph=3D"">What we have:</p><ul class=3D""><li id=3D"5163" class=
=3D"pa pb ij pc b jd pd pe pf jg pg ph pi gf pj pk pl gi pm pn po gl pp pq =
pr ps pt pu pv bh" data-selectable-paragraph=3D"">A two-pane chat UI in the=
 browser, with no build step.</li><li id=3D"171c" class=3D"pa pb ij pc b jd=
 pw pe pf jg px ph pi gf py pk pl gi pz pn po gl qa pq pr ps pt pu pv bh" d=
ata-selectable-paragraph=3D"">A WebSocket connection that streams thinking,=
 content, tool calls, and tool results in real time.</li><li id=3D"969a" cl=
ass=3D"pa pb ij pc b jd pw pe pf jg px ph pi gf py pk pl gi pz pn po gl qa =
pq pr ps pt pu pv bh" data-selectable-paragraph=3D"">Multiple concurrent se=
ssions, each with its own message history.</li><li id=3D"46d9" class=3D"pa =
pb ij pc b jd pw pe pf jg px ph pi gf py pk pl gi pz pn po gl qa pq pr ps p=
t pu pv bh" data-selectable-paragraph=3D"">A skills picker in the sidebar t=
hat loads personas instantly.</li><li id=3D"222b" class=3D"pa pb ij pc b jd=
 pw pe pf jg px ph pi gf py pk pl gi pz pn po gl qa pq pr ps pt pu pv bh" d=
ata-selectable-paragraph=3D"">Slash commands as buttons, for direct control=
 over the session.</li><li id=3D"9872" class=3D"pa pb ij pc b jd pw pe pf j=
g px ph pi gf py pk pl gi pz pn po gl qa pq pr ps pt pu pv bh" data-selecta=
ble-paragraph=3D"">Context warnings at 85%, 90%, and 95%, with automatic co=
mpaction when the limit is hit. The compaction runs in a thread, so the UI =
stays responsive.</li></ul><p id=3D"4553" class=3D"pw-post-body-paragraph p=
